flowchart TD
    A[User enters source + target strings] --> B[Click Visualize]
    B --> C[computeLevenshtein: fill matrix, record steps, compute traceback]
    C --> D[renderMatrix: show empty grid with headers]
    D --> E{User action}
    E -->|Play| F[setInterval: stepForward at speed]
    E -->|Step Forward| G[stepForward: fill next cell with color]
    E -->|Step Backward| H[stepBackward: unfill previous cell]
    E -->|Reset| D
    F --> I{All steps done?}
    G --> I
    I -->|No| E
    I -->|Yes| J[highlightTraceback + show edit distance]
    J --> K{User action}
    K -->|Step Backward| H
    K -->|Reset| D
    K -->|New strings| A
    F -->|Pause| E
